===message:I agree with your idea that we really need to compare the advantages with the disadvatages.  It is really hard to make a concrete decision on such a vast topic when it is so new and not much is really known.  I also think that we really need to get this information that we have found out to the public, though, and get some more opinions.  I don't think very many people are educated in this area, and so it is hard for them to understand what we are really dealing with. 
